text: Anne Elizabeth "Annabeth" Gish (March 13, 1971 near Albuquerque, New Mexico) is a television, movie and stage actress. She has acted in many movies, including Mystic Pizza (1988) and Beautiful Girls (1996). She was born near Albuquerque but was raised near Cedar Falls and Waterloo, Iowa. ==References== Category:Actors from Iowa Category:American movie actors Category:American stage actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Albuquerque, New Mexico Category:People from Cedar Falls, Iowa Category:People from Waterloo, Iowa Category:1971 births Category:Living people
